U.K. Risks Bankruptcy on Pension Promises, Telegraph Reports

-- B y   B l a n c h e   G a t t
-- 
2011-02-23T07:42:59Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-02-23/u-k-risks-bankruptcy-on-pension-promises-telegraph-reports.html
The U.K.’s pension and health-care
commitments put it at “extreme risk” of another economic
crisis unless taxes are raised and spending is cut further, the
 Daily Telegraph  reported, citing the annual Fiscal Risk Index
compiled by risk-assessment company Maplecroft.  To contact the reporter on this story:
